## âš¡ Quick Cheat Sheet

| JHAND Word      | Python Equivalent |
|-----------------|------------------|
| bhenchod        | def              |
| madarchod       | class            |
| bol             | print            |
| agar            | if               |
| warna           | else             |
| jabtak          | while            |
| haramkhor       | for              |
| nikalja         | break            |
| lagateraha      | continue         |
| koshish         | try              |
| phaansi         | except           |
| aakhir          | finally          |
| tez_bhenchod    | async            |

